2136_orig.jpg" class=3D"w-fancybox">
<img src=3D"https://crypto.interactive-maths.com/uploads/1/1/3/4/11345755/2=
32136.jpg?520" alt=3D"Picture" style=3D"width:auto;max-width:100%">
</a>
<div style=3D"display:block;font-size:90%">The Rail Fence Cipher with space=
s left in the message. Colour is used to emphasise where spaces are, agains=
t the blank squares of the table.</div>
</div></div>

<div class=3D"paragraph" style=3D"text-align:justify;">So the ciphertext wo=
uld read "DNHAWXEEDTEES ALF&nbsp; TL".<br></div>

